SUMMARY:Yoga In Nature™\, ALL LEVELS\, Lake Crabtree Community Park
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\n**SPRING IS ALMOST HERE\, so join Yoga In Nature ™** as we do an **ALL LEVELS** vinyasa flow to yin yoga practice\, at this beautiful location\, facing the lake. Modifications provided. **Beginners welcome**. Connect with nature with all of your senses to find calm and peace within as we practice yoga. Yoga heals. Nature heals. Yoga In Nature.\n**Note that location is NOT in the gravel parking lot\, but in the open field:)**\n\nBRING YOUR OWN YOGA MAT\, towel\, water bottle\, and block (if you use one)\, sunscreen\, insect repellent (seasonal). You may also want to bring an old towel or liner for under your mat\, if the ground is wet. We will meet in the open field area near the parking lot. $15/person Accepting Venmo @Darlene-Genander or PayPal dgenander@yogainnature.com or Zelle or cash\n\nLake Crabtree County Park\, past the entrance booth\, at the open field\, near volleyball courts and Old Beech Nature Trail... first right after you enter the park.(If you get to the entrance where there are boat rentals and launch area you've gone too far).\nLake Crabtree County Park\, 1400 Aviation Parkway\, Morrisville
